metadata.name: M.E.N.T.A.L.
metadata.description:
Many the time,
Man folded with a flush,
Many the time,
Man chased that rush,

Eternally, I believe we're meant to be,
Equally, is not what eye see,
Even at the top, will you learn to stop?
Event might happen, to cause a drop,

Nation's eyes, cast to the east,
Nation's fight, because the beast,
Nature echoes, i'm losing to you!
Not alive, what can they do?

Tempers flare, an angry stare,
To someone innocent, you do not care!
Temples destroyed, evil deployed,
To mind does matter, you must employ!

All should be equal,
An Almighty sequel,
Altars await,
All those that have faith,

Less is more to the righteous man,
Learning his lessons, he creates his plan,
Let's all the bad go, through strength not borrowed,
Let's eternal life flow, belief he finally swallowed..........
